Package: sensoreport
Title: Create Reproducible Sensory Reports
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Margot", "Brard", , "margot@thinkr.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6754-0659")),
    person("ThinkR", role = "cph")
  )
Description: A toy Shiny app to query a database in which sensory data are
    stored (sorting task), analyse data R package and generate
    reproducible and interactive HTML sensory reports. Such tool can
    enable sensory analysts and panel leaders to spend less time preparing
    reports, and add more value to their work.
